7-14T01:08:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Psycho 唔好揀hkcc <br />\n揀cccu 先係正確選擇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求指教</blockquote><br />\ncccu入hku psy 一定多過hkcc <br />\n其他唔知"},{"pid":"15c4ab606bd31529b4e26aeef3230c7e07cbbdfb","tid":320603,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Psycho 唔好揀hkcc <br />\n揀cccu 先係正確選擇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求指教</blockquote><br />\ncccu入hku psy 一定多過hkcc <br />\n其他唔知</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>如果想諗住揀心理學又aim兩大麻煩讀CCCU/HKU Space<br />\n<br />\n真實例子：<br />\nCCCU gpa 3.6 -&gt; HKU PSY offer <br />\nHKU Space gpa 3.6 or above -&gt; HKU Social Science Yr3 offer<br />\nHKCC gpa 4.0 -&gt; CU Psy offer<br />\nHkcc要爆哂4先有第2 round既cu offer <br />\n而讀psy要爆4難過登天<br />\n<br />\nPsy基本上non jupas唔睇interview<br />\nHkcc同兩大關係唔好 <br />\n收生一半都係講學院關係<br />\n所以兩大Psy program對hkcc學生要求特別高<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">跪求aim兩大既唔好入hkcc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想再有人中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\ncccu post上面既<br />\n一個hkcc人打"},{"pid":"889ad4cc7540e9b2c783a7655e36aad288cde51c","tid":320603,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屋企有無錢， 無錢唔她讀乞食科<br />\n<br />\n利申asso 上 u psy grad 乞緊食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄有冇諗住讀埋個master做臨床<br />\n貪臨床多錢搵先諗住讀psy幫屋企改善環境</blockquote><br />\n訓醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上clin psy 得hku cu隔年收幾十個 仲要爆4有工作經驗 一係就外國讀 想貪錢多就考紀律部隊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65b37ed221c98b21d5f787c7e813b4a4733c145","tid":320603,"uid":64378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屋企有無錢， 無錢唔她讀乞食科<br />\n<br />\n利申asso 上 u psy grad 乞緊食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄有冇諗住讀埋個master做臨床<br />\n貪臨床多錢搵先諗住讀psy幫屋企改善環境</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己諗下 master 學費幾錢，讀個陣開支點算，識唔識賣屎忽討好lecturer , 入左去gpa 唔夠top 又有咩退路，同埋clin psy 對住一堆唔開心既csse ,處理差d 都影響人一世，為錢就過主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇你竟然會貪clin psy 多錢去讀都知你係on9 個堆，讀第二科啦呢科on9 仔讀完會更on9唔岩你， 我成個asso +degree carry on9仔最少三十個，on9底入呢科真係只會累人累己， 要錢死去三寶nursing 工程會計個邊啦<br />\n<br />\npsychology 出名乞食，你同我講為錢讀呢科，真係人唔笑狗都吠，因為真係太on9所以屌得比較狼，唔好意思，已經有好多粉腸同19黎呢科厄飯食害死client, 所以真係過主唔該"}]}